Interface AbiChromatogramFileVisitor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ChromatogramFileVisitor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbiChromatogramBuilder.AbiChromatogramBuilderVisitor

    public interface AbiChromatogramFileVisitor
extends ChromatogramFileVisitor
    AbiChromatogramFileVisitor is an ABI Chromatogram specific implementation of ChromatogramFileVisitor.

    dkatzel
